channel.description:
Oneindia is a large online portal that brings Breaking & Latest current news headlines from india on Politics, Sports, Current Affairs in India & around the world. Latest updates on Indian sports, movies, business, stock markets, Cricket, lifestyle & much more.

This channel having 3rd party videos shared by PR/Media/Production houses and Advertising Agencies.  Videos uploaded on this channel only after giving due credits to the team that has worked on it. 

In case of objection to any video content uploaded on this channel, please write to shiv.kant@oneindia.co.in or you can send your feedback on http://www.oneindia.com/feedback.php
